Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.67,0:00:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失火了，快點滅火
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.34,0:00:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有賊，賊人入侵了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.97,0:00:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往陛下的寢室去了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.24,0:00:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來人，快來人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.15,0:00:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是奴獸，是奴獸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.69,0:00:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應戰，快應戰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.33,0:00:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.60,0:00:37.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快找，快找出來！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.35,0:00:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.33,0:01:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠近馳名的蒼天之青玉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.00,0:01:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去乙HiME的能力後\N也只剩這點本事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.47,0:01:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又撲空了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.60,0:01:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也罷，我也不認為\N這麼容易可以找到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.30,0:01:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是庫拉克
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.34,0:01:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫拉克耶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.27,0:01:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫拉克？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.61,0:01:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔，有東西掉在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.11,0:02:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小子，那是垃圾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.85,0:02:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦，是好大的垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.12,0:02:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是庫拉克啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.78,0:02:06.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實是庫拉克
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.65,0:02:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫拉克似乎可以帶來好運呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.72,0:02:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀，什麼樣的？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.66,0:02:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,替男女結緣啊，就像現在這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.20,0:02:17.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是在說什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.74,0:02:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.38,0:02:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來想請它救救我的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.12,0:02:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.32,0:02:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.72,0:02:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來救救我啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.17,0:03:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找到夢想了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.47,0:03:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內心悸動無法平息
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.52,0:03:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寶物誕生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.06,0:03:22.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滿盈內心 開始散放光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.23,0:03:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何會如此不安呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.90,0:03:33.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法控制的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.57,0:03:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓人不禁落淚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.05,0:03:45.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有朝一日一定會抵達
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.99,0:03:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算中途受挫也不放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.23,0:03:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼓起勇氣向前邁進
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.23,0:04:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能踏出小小的一步 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.87,0:04:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是嶄新的我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.18,0:04:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第1話 夢之☆愛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.70,0:04:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.50,0:04:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是珊瑚第一名
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.90,0:04:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜·王小姐吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.63,0:04:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃，我沒有點這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.10,0:04:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那邊的客人請的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.57,0:04:42.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬未來的乙HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.58,0:04:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬美麗的乙HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.78,0:04:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬乙HiME…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.38,0:04:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.58,0:04:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.09,0:04:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝…謝謝各位
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.35,0:04:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.77,0:05:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮依娜，怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.05,0:05:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.35,0:05:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮依娜，呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.85,0:05:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳的腳…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.09,0:05:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有種不祥的預感
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.49,0:05:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定真的猜中了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.70,0:05:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下禮拜就是\N公主的即位典禮了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.07,0:05:42.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎已經有好幾個人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.74,0:05:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潛入溫德市了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.30,0:05:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好個黑團
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.61,0:05:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明知道我們雖然近在咫尺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.44,0:05:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但因為與溫德市之間的\N條約限制而不得出手干涉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.28,0:05:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年應該會有很多動作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.48,0:05:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟是那件事之後第14年
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.62,0:06:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我們卻還沒找到“她”
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.46,0:06:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才請靜留回來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.36,0:06:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,替學園盡力也是我們五柱的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.83,0:06:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加爾德羅貝的立場總是很微妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.47,0:06:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正不管怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.24,0:06:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也只能等出事之後\N才急忙對應了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.07,0:06:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.78,0:06:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽妳抱怨也是我的工作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.75,0:06:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學園長
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.36,0:06:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親，非常對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.86,0:06:41.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在眾人面前丟那種臉…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.03,0:06:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.96,0:06:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是意外
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.83,0:06:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不幸的意外啊，妮依娜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.80,0:06:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一場不幸的意外！父親…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.27,0:06:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.71,0:06:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.41,0:06:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了，這個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.51,0:07:02.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有謝謝妳剛剛的果汁，妮依娜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.02,0:07:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.68,0:07:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.85,0:07:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有父親可以叫我妮依娜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.39,0:07:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.73,0:07:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.13,0:07:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.83,0:07:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少校
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.93,0:07:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到本國出差辛苦您了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.97,0:07:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜，辛苦妳來接我了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.60,0:07:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.14,0:07:27.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.84,0:07:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直覺得妳像什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.91,0:07:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.41,0:07:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像螞蟻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.25,0:07:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螞蟻？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.38,0:07:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要叫我螞蟻啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.85,0:07:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫愛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.05,0:07:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢宮愛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.15,0:07:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真是失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.79,0:07:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是駐阿爾泰公國大使館武官
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.29,0:07:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝爾蓋·王
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.59,0:07:50.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭螞蟻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.30,0:07:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更討厭別人叫我螞蟻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.53,0:07:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼不好吧，螞蟻愛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.34,0:07:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等，果汁的謝禮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.07,0:07:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.97,0:08:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.31,0:08:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以這樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.21,0:08:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婆婆說過受人恩惠就要報答…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.95,0:08:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也不要跟著我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.51,0:08:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礙事，礙眼，煩死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.72,0:08:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.79,0:08:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳很煩耶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.09,0:08:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要大聲叫我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.17,0:08:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.64,0:08:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.71,0:08:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車票…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.12,0:08:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要收好啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.36,0:08:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去拿了水，要喝嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.96,0:08:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣，很丟臉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.90,0:09:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜妳生什麼氣啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.93,0:09:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託妳別跟我說話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.32,0:09:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是城堡耶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.52,0:09:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡面應該有公主吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.42,0:09:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼樣的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.86,0:09:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒人知道，又還沒即位
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.50,0:09:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主…公主…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.37,0:09:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.84,0:09:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的，又跑不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.84,0:09:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經派搜索隊去鎮上找了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.08,0:09:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思，總是麻煩你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.97,0:10:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，我在趕時間
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.77,0:10:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂，妮娜妳等等嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.57,0:10:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.51,0:10:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思，從現在起\N妳可不可以自己想辦法？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.25,0:10:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.15,0:10:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳知不知道\N叫做加爾德羅貝的學校在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.25,0:10:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳找學園有什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.92,0:10:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在找我的媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.23,0:10:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我只知道\N她以前是一位乙HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.33,0:10:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加爾德羅貝\N是乙HiME的學校對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.17,0:10:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以如果\N我也當上乙HiME的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.30,0:10:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.27,0:10:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.70,0:10:46.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳什麼都不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.07,0:10:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從哪裡來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.37,0:10:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葛雷利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.18,0:10:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道那是哪個鄉下地方啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.34,0:10:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是妳完全不瞭解乙HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.32,0:10:58.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂喂，那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.95,0:10:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電視
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.42,0:11:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.52,0:11:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本國溫德布倫在這一帶\N保有最多地球時代的技術…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.39,0:11:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人是公主？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.56,0:11:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是，那一位是乙HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.23,0:11:15.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Meister靜留姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.17,0:11:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.54,0:11:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mei…Meister…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.67,0:11:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.18,0:11:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂，這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.42,0:11:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全像投影
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.42,0:11:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，那個也是？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.79,0:11:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.45,0:11:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害喔，好像魔法一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.56,0:11:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.16,0:11:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個也是全像投影？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.46,0:11:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對對，一切都是全像投…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.81,0:11:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想抓到我還早一百年啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.75,0:12:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.20,0:12:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.36,0:12:18.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追過了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.16,0:12:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.01,0:12:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會折壽…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.38,0:12:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.89,0:12:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.62,0:12:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做…做得好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.96,0:12:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,值得讚賞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.96,0:12:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.26,0:12:53.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那女孩還來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.10,0:12:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們聽好，幫助我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.64,0:12:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些人是壞人，是綁架犯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.77,0:13:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.57,0:13:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟…糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.81,0:13:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是婆婆說過的無法之徒～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.18,0:13:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著，我們是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.36,0:13:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.73,0:13:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜妳好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.03,0:13:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我問妳，剛剛那個女生呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.04,0:13:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.21,0:13:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉呀呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.42,0:13:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們居然讓她跑了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.59,0:13:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這些蠢才
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.83,0:13:55.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主下週就要即位了…\N公主真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.99,0:13:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定認為這是最後一次機會…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.66,0:13:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳說是不是呀，命\N把她找出來！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.60,0:14:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何都要把她找出來！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.47,0:14:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來是沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.27,0:14:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.28,0:14:13.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.58,0:14:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機場遺跡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.98,0:14:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機場？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.18,0:14:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳什麼都不知道耶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.88,0:14:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是過去可以在天上飛的機器\N停泊的地方啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.69,0:14:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人，這種東西可以飛？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.72,0:14:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像鳥一樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.16,0:14:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太神奇了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.89,0:14:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,濕答答的真難過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.63,0:14:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰拿件衣服給我換吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.46,0:14:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這給妳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.56,0:14:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要，那個好髒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.27,0:14:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛，我們特地救了妳耶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.80,0:14:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婆婆說過\N不知報恩的人最容易遭到報應
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.07,0:14:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳這個沒禮貌的說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.08,0:14:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.01,0:14:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.01,0:14:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經夠了吧\N剩下的事情自己解決
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.01,0:14:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著，妳給我慢著
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.58,0:14:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳要丟下我走嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.58,0:14:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的外出時間已經結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.49,0:14:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.45,0:14:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.66,0:14:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.62,0:15:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們應該是\N服侍王宮貴族的裝飾花朵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.29,0:15:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就來服侍我啊，快
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.53,0:15:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請原諒我的無禮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.30,0:15:10.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮…妮娜\N不用跟這種人道歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.97,0:15:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳真的什麼都不知道耶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.21,0:15:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些加爾德羅貝的乙HiME們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.41,0:15:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡是沒辦法\N在我們面前抬起頭的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.61,0:15:20.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙HiME？妳說妮娜？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.19,0:15:33.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵從黑色誓約，我將實現盟約
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.69,0:15:36.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古代之光，知識與智慧之神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.80,0:15:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請賜我忠實的奴僕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.37,0:15:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳說她是乙HiME…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.41,0:15:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.18,0:15:51.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奴獸？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.11,0:15:51.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.88,0:15:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牠盯上我了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.65,0:16:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.30,0:16:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳…妳想想辦法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.30,0:16:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳並不是我的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.77,0:16:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果打倒牠，父親就…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.31,0:16:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.38,0:16:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓妳以我暫時主人的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.14,0:16:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請給我使用舞鬥服的認證
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.05,0:16:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認證？妳是說那個？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.91,0:16:30.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯，快點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.78,0:16:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳叫什麼名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.25,0:16:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜·王
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.42,0:16:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧，妮娜·王
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.22,0:16:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擁有珊瑚貴石的吾之乙HiME啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.39,0:16:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以吾之名解放汝之力量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.96,0:16:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，主人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.26,0:16:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物質化！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.09,0:17:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.76,0:17:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奴獸？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.09,0:17:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒弄錯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.56,0:17:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的，而且在同一個地點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.77,0:17:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也出現了珊瑚第一名妮娜·王\N展開舞鬥服的反應
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.80,0:17:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了，妳繼續監視，主任
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.61,0:17:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑團來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.21,0:17:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在溫德市
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.68,0:17:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我們的學生以舞鬥服應戰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.58,0:17:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣違反條約
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.65,0:17:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀，如果是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.75,0:17:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,附近應該有人可以給她認證
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.02,0:17:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在溫德能做到這個的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.66,0:17:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.66,0:17:47.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.73,0:17:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就彼此彼此了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.43,0:17:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下就有藉口插手了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.80,0:17:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，出動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.70,0:17:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討伐黑團
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.37,0:17:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以借我一個人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.28,0:18:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算集中力量，光靠珊瑚舞鬥服…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.82,0:18:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的，我生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.89,0:18:16.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等，那是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.72,0:18:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.20,0:18:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然沒用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.70,0:18:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳幹什麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.96,0:18:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣不是讓牠更生氣了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.57,0:18:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.47,0:18:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.72,0:18:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經通知城內的人避難了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.45,0:18:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.25,0:18:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睽違50年的實戰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.63,0:18:57.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茜負責救出妮娜和公主
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.10,0:18:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，學園長
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.20,0:19:01.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜留負責殲滅奴獸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.93,0:19:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.74,0:19:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.34,0:19:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放寬心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.40,0:19:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，靜留姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.41,0:19:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.02,0:19:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是作夢吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.42,0:19:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那個GEM的力量嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.22,0:19:26.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.93,0:19:29.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊，人變得跟豆子一樣小了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.57,0:20:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.07,0:20:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茜姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.94,0:20:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來想在航空公園迎戰…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.64,0:20:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到竟然會降落在市街上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.71,0:20:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.52,0:20:30.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嬌嫣的紫水晶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.02,0:20:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Meister靜留·維奧拉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.66,0:20:34.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙HiME出面作戰？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.09,0:20:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.93,0:20:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了…掃除時間到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.28,0:20:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,額頭上面有東西喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.22,0:21:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.16,0:21:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奴獸出現
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.93,0:21:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睽違半世紀的乙HiME實戰…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.63,0:21:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會演變成大事件啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.90,0:21:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.20,0:21:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看見了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.40,0:21:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要追嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.67,0:21:20.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好讓所有人\N從城裡面出來避難了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.34,0:21:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是公主看到\N不知道會說什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.58,0:21:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒，好棒喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.25,0:21:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個，該怎麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.52,0:21:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是乙HiME的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.49,0:21:41.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,培養乙HiME的是加爾德羅貝\N就是這間學園
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.53,0:21:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加爾德羅貝…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.26,0:21:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.43,0:21:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.10,0:21:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜，妳沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.93,0:21:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唷，妳也沒事…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.10,0:21:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼天的青玉？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.98,0:22:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帥喔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.05,0:22:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要當上乙HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.85,0:22:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要當上！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.96,0:22:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇氣會實現願望 Do your best
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.73,0:22:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別認輸 向前邁進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.60,0:22:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只等著我的故事 現在開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.52,0:22:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其逃避 不如挺身面對更好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.33,0:22:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是少女的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.53,0:22:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很努力唷\N就算內心突然感到寂寞的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.00,0:23:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要以笑容面對
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.94,0:23:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼NO NO NO 你的世界裡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.98,0:23:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定有快樂的未來 我想守護你
